.SH DESCRIPTION
.I Xneko
D 2
displays a window in which a cat chases your "mouse" cursor.  Try
moving the mouse inside and outside the
.I xneko
window, leaving it stationary, moving it slowly and quickly, etc., and
watch the cat respond.
